wwwsamgroupcomensustainabilityinsightsamcorporatesustainabilityassessmentjsp  httpwwwfoeeuropeorgfoeewhysustainabilitycriteriainbanking  httpwwwsamgroupcomeninvestmentfundssustainabilitythemeinvestinginvestmentphilosophyprocessjsp  httpglobalepsoncomnewsroomnewshtm  httpwwwclimatechangeawardsorgukstaticwinners  httpwwwefinancialnewseventscomawardassetmanagementwinnershtml  httpwwwsamgroupcomenaboutusawardsjsp  httpwwwsamgroupcomenaboutusfactsandfiguresjsp  httpwwwunpriorgsignatories  httpwwweurosiforgnetworklistofmemberaffiliates  httpwwwasriaorgmembershiplist  httpwwwsustainablech  httpwwwbruggerconsultingchenphtml  httpwwwasriaorgnewspress external linksedit httpwwwrobecosamcom retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerobecosamoldid categories investment companies of switzerland establishments in switzerlandhidden categories articles lacking reliable references from november all articles lacking reliable referencesarticles needing additional references from november all articles needing additional referencesarticles with a promotional tone from november all articles with a promotional tonepages using deprecated image syntaxall articles with links needing disambiguationarticles with links needing disambiguation from june  navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages add links this page was last edited on  july  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikiped