ain talent or enhance its operational ecoefficiency matter from an investor’s point of view because they impact a company’s competitive position and longterm financial performance find a company show all robecosam gold class robecosam silver class robecosam bronze class robecosam industry mover distinction company industry country m co industrial conglomerates united states abbott laboratories health care equipment  supplies united states abbvie inc biotechnology united states abertis infraestructuras sa transportation and transportation infrastructure spain abnamro holding nv banks netherlands accenture plc it services  internet software and services united states acciona sa electric utilities spain accor sa hotels resorts  cruise lines france acs actividades de construccion y servicios sa construction  engineering spain actelion ltd biotechnology switzerland adidas ag textiles apparel  luxury goods germany adobe systems inc software united states advanced semiconductor engineering inc semiconductors  semiconductor equipment taiwan aegon nv insurance netherlands aeon co ltd food  staples retailing japan aeroports de paris transportation and transportation infrastructure france agilent technologies inc life sciences tools  services united states air franceklm airlines france air liquide sa chemicals france ajinomoto co inc food products japan akzo nobel nv chemicals netherlands alcoa inc aluminum united states allianz se insurance germany alstom sa machinery and electrical equipment france altagas ltd oil  gas storage  transportation canada amadeus it group sa it services  internet software and services spain amcor ltdaustralia containers  packaging australia amorepacific corp personal products south korea ana holdings inc airlines japan anglo american plc metals  mining united kingdom anglogold ashanti ltd metals  mining south africa asics corp textiles apparel  luxury goods japan asml holding nv semiconductors  semiconductor equipment netherlands assicurazioni gen